    bool "Use microseconds for Bluetooth debug time"
    default n
    depends on BLUETOOTH_DEBUG_TIMEVAL
    help
        Enable this option to use microseconds (us) for Bluetooth debug time.
        If disabled, milliseconds (ms) will be used by default.

